---
title: Butterflied Chicken with Green Bean and Wholegrain Mustard Potato Salad
description: Potato salad is a summer staple but this one is a bit special. We've added some green beans for colour and given it a kick with grain mustard. Apparently in 1336 the Duke of Burgundy gave a banquet for the King of France and provided 70 gallons of mustard sauce. We know that a little goes a long way so haven't sent you quite that much but hope you enjoy the excitement it brings to tonight's dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/butterflied-chicken-wk-34-a856eea3.jpg
